title: 810. Daniel Jeremiah's Final Mock Draft
itunes:title: 810. Daniel Jeremiah's Final Mock Draft
description:
Daniel Jeremiah is back with a new episode of Move the Sticks from the 2022 NFL Draft with special guests Rich Eisen and Charles Davis. On this special show, DJ gives a breakdown of his final mock draft. Find out which quarterbacks will go in the first round, which position group is the deepest and if there are any surprise players that will sneak into the first round.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
